00:04:03.448 --> 00:04:11.100
As you know, Bhagavad Gita explained,
how Shri Krishna showed the Virata to Arjuna.

00:04:11.534 --> 00:04:18.450
And then when Arjuna sees whatever was
contained in Krishna, he panicked completely.

00:04:18.650 --> 00:04:24.420
He said, I mean, sorry, I really know. I mean,
please forgive me for calling you my friend.

00:04:24.939 --> 00:04:29.180
Forgive me for joking with you, for eating
with you, for, I didn't know. Please forgive me.

00:04:29.380 --> 00:04:31.660
